      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «مَنْ أَنْفَقَ دِرْهَماً فِي اَلْحَجِّ كَانَ خَيْراً لَهُ مِنْ مِائَةِ أَلْفِ دِرْهَمٍ يُنْفِقُهَا فِي حَقٍّ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2247 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"Whoever spends a dirham on Hajj, it is better for them than spending one hundred thousand dirhams on a rightful cause.\""
        ]
      }
    },
